# Google Fonts Developer API key — enables the full searchable font list.
# Get a free key: https://developers.google.com/fonts/docs/developer_api
#   1. Create/select a project in https://console.cloud.google.com/
#   2. Enable the "Web Fonts Developer API"
#   3. Create an API key under "APIs & Services > Credentials"
# Copy this file to .env.local and paste your key below.
# Without a key the app falls back to a small curated list of popular fonts.
VITE_GOOGLE_FONTS_API_KEY=
